 <span data-ttu-id="a9687-358">연결된 된 개체에서 사용할 수 있는 속성 및 메서드를 확인 하려면이 속성을 사용할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a9687-358">You can use this property to find out what properties and methods are available on the associated object.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a9687-359">다음 예제는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.SchemaClassName%2A> 및 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.SchemaEntry%2A> 의 속성을 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> 클래스입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a9687-359">The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.SchemaClassName%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.SchemaEntry%2A> properties of the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a9687-360">이 예제에서는 사용자 지정을 가져옵니다 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> 개체 및 해당 자식을 모두 경우 가져옵니다는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.SchemaEntry%2A> 개체가 컨테이너 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a9687-360">This example gets the user-specified <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> object and gets all of its children if the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.SchemaEntry%2A> object is a container object.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a9687-361"><xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.SchemaEntry%2A> 경우에 컨테이너 개체는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Name%2A> 해당 개체의 "컨테이너인".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a9687-361">The <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.SchemaEntry%2A> is a container object if the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Name%2A> of that object is "container".</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Dim myADSPath As String = "LDAP://onecity/CN=Users,DC=onecity,DC=corp,DC=fabrikam,DC=com"  
  
