## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a9687-375">설정할 수 있습니다 합니다 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> 고 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> Active Directory Domain Services의 정보에 액세스할 수 있는 대체 자격 증명을 지정 하려면.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a9687-375">You can set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> in order to specify alternate credentials with which to access the information in Active Directory Domain Services.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a9687-376">다른 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> 인스턴스에서이 개체 검색 (예를 통해 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>) 동일한 대체 자격 증명을 사용 하 여 자동으로 만들어집니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a9687-376">Any other <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> objects retrieved from this instance (for example, through <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>) are automatically created with the same alternate credentials.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a9687-377">다음 예제는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> 및 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> 의 속성을 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> 클래스입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a9687-377">The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> properties of the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a9687-378">이 예제에서는 사용자 지정을 가져옵니다 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> 하며 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> 모든 해당 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a9687-378">This example gets the user-specified <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> of all its <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Dim myADSPath As String = _  
      "LDAP://onecity/CN=Users,DC=onecity,DC=corp,DC=fabrikam,DC=com"  
  
' Create an Instance of DirectoryEntry.  
Dim myDirectoryEntry As New DirectoryEntry(myADSPath)  
myDirectoryEntry.Username = UserName  
myDirectoryEntry.Password = SecurelyStoredPassword  
  
' Get the Child ADS objects.  
Console.WriteLine("The Child ADS objects are:")  
Dim myChildDirectoryEntry As DirectoryEntry  
For Each myChildDirectoryEntry In  myDirectoryEntry.Children  
   Console.WriteLine(myChildDirectoryEntry.Path)  
Next myChildDirectoryEntry  
```  
  
```csharp  
